2018/06/21
Specification (Draft)
An IOT device with N sensors that are capable to transmit their data to a cloud service which will register the transaction on a blockchain. Each device has a unique universal ID.
The block chain will record transactions coming from devices.

Plan/AR
1. [MM] Evaluate existing IOT HW devices with sensors and WiFi or 4G (5G) data capability. Recommend one.
2. [YS] Evaluate cloud services that can process IOT data. Recommend one.
3. [KD] Evaluate blockchain framework that can record transactions. Recommend one.

